{
  "stem": "24231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I came with a transport, AAQ, and my number was AAQ463.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And, and we came to this [NON-ENGLISH], which is in German, [GERMAN], and in Czech.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were assembled in Prague.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There used to be an exhibition palace, they called it an exhibition palace, in Prague, which they converted into a section where they-- all the Jews would come in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then from there, then they would ship them into this Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when you were allowed to take, I guess, two bags of-- they put us into cattle wagons, and, and we traveled to-- My grandmother also, who was, at that time 80 years old, she was unable to walk.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So they brought in a moving van.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the poor woman, when she got into the assembly area, she was all, all banged up because she-- they put her on a chair.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And as the moving van was going around, she fell down and she was going from wall to wall.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she was all banged up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so my father was trying to, you know, bandage her up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This transport was the whole family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was my, my father, my mother, my sister and myself, and my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole building where we were just was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe four hours or something like this because we were stopping all over the place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But maybe four, maybe five hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we-- when we arrived, what happened there were SS men there and Czech gendarmes were over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- we went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they took most of the-- there was some Jewish guys also, these guys who were-- young guys-- with little two-wheel wagons.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
